# External URLs that are known to fail for automated checkers but work for humans.
# Review these quarterly and remove entries that start succeeding or have been replaced.

# EBU publishes loudness recommendations at this URL but blocks bot user-agents with 403.
# Accessible to humans; lychee gets bot-blocked.
^https://tech\.ebu\.ch/

# YouTube restructures support paths frequently. The howyoutubeworks URL has moved,
# but we keep it in foundations/video.md for now. TODO: find the current canonical URL.
^https://www\.youtube\.com/howyoutubeworks/

# The private Verdigris www repo. Unauthenticated GitHub Actions GITHUB_TOKEN cannot
# access private repos, so this 404s in CI. The link works for team members.
^https://github\.com/VerdigrisTech/verdigris($|/)

# BBC Subtitle Guidelines: the github.io redirect chain sometimes fails. The guidelines
# exist at bbc.co.uk or are linked from the main BBC accessibility pages. TODO: verify
# canonical URL and update foundations/video.md citation.
^https://bbc\.github\.io/subtitle-guidelines/
